{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 201435, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "朋友圈里说的啥，好奇", "timestamp": 1596327530, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201439, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得不出意外的话，会的，随着国家经济的发展，分配制度的改革，法制和人权的完善，西方价值体系下的人会越来越认识到我国政体的正当性和合理性，台湾人对统一的抗拒也会减弱吧", "timestamp": 1596327668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201440, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 他们可不这样认为", "timestamp": 1596327709, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201443, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得会 但那时候是不是shzy就不好说了\n", "timestamp": 1596327822, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201444, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "要岛不要人", "timestamp": 1596327829, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201445, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本质是中美问题 解决了中美问题台湾就不是个事儿", "timestamp": 1596327845, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201448, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 老yxt了", "timestamp": 1596327955, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201449, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 正当性还说得过去 毕竟没有gcd没有xzg 然而我国政体合理性何在啊", "timestamp": 1596328052, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201451, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 保护隐私，不挂了", "timestamp": 1596328257, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201459, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 正是因为台湾地区受到西方价值观深远的影响，所以我觉得这件事并没有这么简单。不是说随着大陆的逐渐强大、法制的完善，他们就会认同大陆。如果想要达到这一点，至少还需要西方世界力量的衰弱。而实际上呢？今天无论是经济上还是文化上，依然是西方在主导世界。甚至大陆地区也不可避免的受到种种影响。", "timestamp": 1596328547, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201474, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "必有一战，文化是根本。", "timestamp": 1596329511, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201477, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就算两岸想统一，西方人也不同意。东德西德是因为德国人不想统一？世界霸主拦着不让嘛。", "timestamp": 1596329619, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201483, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中国比外蒙古领先那么多，清朝时候中国和蒙古也是统一的，蒙古人想加入中国吗？我看没人想", "timestamp": 1596329746, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201498, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "台湾是历史固有领土，外蒙也是历史固有领土。但是台湾经济发达，战略位置重要，获取台湾就等于突破了第一岛链，所以优先解决，由于需要俄罗斯盟友共同对抗美国，所以外蒙问题相当长的时期不会提。", "timestamp": 1596330633, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201503, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 外蒙不是已经是独立国家了吗，也可以收回吗？", "timestamp": 1596330832, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201515, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 当中国稳坐世界一哥的时候，也可以像美国突袭伊拉克一样，随便找个莫须有的理由把外面的外蒙收回。但是蒙古太穷，主要是对俄罗斯战略防御价值大，现在老大是美国，老二老三还在同盟，没有收回的必要。", "timestamp": 1596331358, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201529, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 有了外蒙还可以有战略缓冲，没必要收回吧", "timestamp": 1596331726, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201537, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 互为战略缓冲地，取决于谁强谁弱，现在这样有利于维持两国稳定，收回蒙古是大大后期的事了。现在主要考虑收回台湾，关键在于怎么收回。", "timestamp": 1596332066, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 201974, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 36241, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感觉要收回得尽快了，等到他们上一代人都死了之后就真的和我们没啥关系了", "timestamp": 1596342381, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 36241, "reply": 19, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "#政治相关#\n从各种因素来看，台湾最终是否会回归大陆？\n看一位台湾同学朋友圈有感\n理性讨论", "timestamp": 1596327330, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782600, "url": "", "vote": {}}}